text: Kadhim Kamil (born 1 July 1951) is a former Iraqi football forward who played for Iraq in the 1974 Asian Games and 1976 AFC Asian Cup. Hesham played for the national team in 1976. ==References== Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Iraq international footballers Category:1976 AFC Asian Cup players Category:Living people Category:Association football defenders Category:1951 births
